snippet.title: SMBX2 Beta 5 | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The new version of SMBX2 is out now! Enjoy this quick overview over some of the features you can play with in SMBX2 Beta 5!

SMBX2 Website: http://codehaus.moe/
Codehaus Discord: https://discord.gg/aCZqadJ

Music:
